data.description: STOP! Don't miss out on this Beautiful Home in The Lakes at Rancho El Dorado community. Live comfortably in this spacious 4 bedroom 3 bathroom house with an extra-large lot big enough for a pool. Upgraded open concept kitchen with granite countertops and large kitchen island. Lots of cabinet space and stainless steel appliances. Home also includes an extra-large loft and den. Save money with this energy efficient home with spray foam insulation and PAID OFF solar system. Bills average only $110 per month with a large family. Also includes a soft water system and special ozone system to eliminate using laundry soap.  Over $30,000 in upgrades including remodeled master bathroom, sealed ac ducts with 2 ion air scrubbers to eliminate allergies. RO system and updated water heater. Call Today
